Package lab3_1

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileManager
    Utility class for initializing the database for tools and suppliers.
    Inventory
    Inventory maintains the list of tools in the shop.
    Order
    Order stores a collection of order line.
    OrderLine
    Order Line consists of information for the order of a tool item that is low in stock.
    Shop
    Shop communicates with the front end (ShopApp) and keep as record the inventory of tools and the supplier list.
    ShopApp
    Shop application to manage the inventory of tools that it sells.
    Supplier
    Represent a tool supplier and keeps track of its id, company name, address, and sale contact.
    SupplierList
    Supplier maintains the list of suppliers.
    Tool
    Represent a tool item and keeps track of its id, name, quantity in stock, price, and supplier id.
